Package com.charliai.activities.api

Class Interaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.charliai.activities.api.Interaction
  • public class Interaction
extends java.lang.Object
    The Interaction class supports all the processing and in-memory storage of interaction detail (i.e. the details associated with conversations. TODO: Update the error handling on missing data, or the data is optional
